HEADWORD: Effume
<hw>Ef*fume"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>effumare</ets> to emit smoke; <ets>ex</ets> + <ets>fumare</ets> to
smoke, fr. <ets>fumus</ets> smoke.]</ety> <def>To breathe or puff
out.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
